        "setup": "Create or sign in to a DaniWeb account, then register an app from [Manage Your Apps](https://www.daniweb.com/connect/developers/apps/register). The developer docs say you must register your application and then use OAuth 2.0 to obtain access tokens for API calls. During OAuth, use your app's `client_id` and chosen `redirect_uri`, send users to `https://www.daniweb.com/connect/oauth/auth`, and exchange the returned code at `https://www.daniweb.com/connect/oauth/access_token` for a temporary access token. Access tokens expire after 24 hours according to the docs.",
